*xf86-video-intel-2.21.14 (13 Aug 2013)

  13 Aug 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +xf86-video-intel-2.21.14.ebuild, -xf86-video-intel-2.21.9.ebuild:
  Bump to latest. Remove dri useflag, since --enable-dri pulls in
  both DRI1 and DRI2 support, and DRI1 is exclusive with kms-only.

