*xf86-video-intel-2.15.0-r1 (07 Jul 2011)

  07 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  xf86-video-intel-2.15.0-r1.ebuild,
  +files/xf86-video-intel-2.15-no-udev.patch,
  +files/xf86-video-intel-2.15-no-cached-pixmap-locations.patch:
  Initial overlay import. Remove dependency on udev. Nullify
  the effects of commit 'f3a47d7...' on 20101206 ('Cache pixmap
  binding locations'), since it causes rendering glitches in
  GTK pixmaps on CLIP.
